        "action": "5 year passport confiscation for people who cause trouble and fights on planes",
        "additional_details": "We think not enough is being done to convince people of the need to behave in this confined space. We believe punishment of passport confiscation would make people think twice.",
        "background": "Anyone who has caused trouble on plane journeys that results in police waiting on landing or diversions to other airports should have their passport confiscated for 5 years.",
